text: Vasileios Tsolakidis () (born 9 September 1979) is a Greek gymnast. He competed in the men's parallel bars event at the 2012 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Greek male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Greece Category:Gymnasts at the 2012 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Thessaloniki
